Usage

  The following examples describe the basic usage of the CRX Maven
  Plugin.

* Use as part of a composite project

  You can use the CRX Maven Plugin as part of a composite project.

  +---------------------------------------
  <project>
  <packaging>war</packaging>
  <plugin>
  <groupId>com.btmatthews.maven.plugins</groupId>
  <artifactId>crx-maven-plugin</artifactId>
  <version>${project.version}</version>
  <configuration>
  <pemFile>..</pemFile>
  <pemPassword>...</pemPassword>
  </configuration>
  </plugin>
  </plugins>
  </build>
  </project>
  +---------------------------------------

